## <a id="reqs"></a> Requirements

You will need an existing Ruxit environment when specifying your service plans.

## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

The Dynatrace Ruxit Agent is bundled with the Java buildpack version 3.8 available on PivNet (as of June 2016). The bundled Agent version is 1.95. Dynatrace recommends you to use the latest version of Ruxit Agent so please overwrite the default version to be used with `version: 1.+`. 

Future releases of Dynatrace Ruxit for PCF will support Node.js and PHP buildpacks.

